{"tid":735623,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"💳 信用卡討論區 (41) 貼link死全家 年費免問 發問前睇#1","createTime":"2018-07-09T15:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T00:31:11.000Z","uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f6819129e54d0dee3103435aa1d966bcd9742da1","tid":735623,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:30:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins>目錄</ins><br />\n<br />\n#1 FAQ<br />\n#2 集中討論卡種<br />\n#3 大學生懶人包<br />\n#4 教學<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">借定唔借，還得到先好借！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<em>世上冇免費午餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學賺回贈前，先爬文做功課 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </em></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#1 FAQ</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ：年薪 $1,000,000 申請咩卡好？<br />\nA：八達通卡<br />\n<br />\nQ：想求 Member-Get-Member (MGM) 推薦連結應該點做？<br />\nA：留低自己嘅聯絡分式 (e.g. Telegram)，<span style=\"color: red;\">重申本 post 嚴禁貼 MGM link</span><br />\n<br />\nQ：點申請年費豁免？<br />\nA：(1) 先致電年費豁免或客戶服務熱線 (2) 如未能豁免可考慮取消信用卡<br />\n<em>(收年費後一個月內取消，卡行一定會回水)</em><br />\n<br />\nQ：邊張卡啱我用／回贈高啲？<br />\nA：消費習慣因人而異，請自行比較<br />\n<br />\nQ：邊張卡 O! ePay／PayMe／WeChat Pay／支付寶HK 有分？<br />\nA：Google<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：八達通自動增值 (AAVS)、網上繳費用邊張好？<br />\nA：睇<ins>集中討論卡種</ins><br />\n<br />\nQ：迎新／推廣嘅里數／積分／回贈幾時先有？<br />\nA：睇 T&amp;C<br />\n<br />\nQ：點解有啲卡你地唔講嘅？<br />\nA：狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">渣打</div></span></strong></span><br />\nQ：究竟 PayMe／WeChat Pay／支付寶HK 有冇分？<br />\nA：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">安信</div></span></strong></span><br />\nQ：有冇得申請返 Visa？<br />\nA：<a href=\"https://m.primecredit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/WeWa-Visa-PDF-form-FA.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.primecredit.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2FWeWa-Visa-PDF-form-FA.pdf&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=36906603\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.primecredit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/WeWa-Visa-PDF-form-FA.pdf</a> (適用於全新／現有客戶)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">實用 Link</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n💳 信用卡討論區 (38) 貼link搵食過主 年費免問 發問前睇post頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/686461/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/686461/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nApple Pay: 特約銀行和發卡機構<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT206638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-hk%2FHT206638&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=58cd5c24\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT206638</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Pay： 合作銀行<br />\n<a href=\"https://pay.google.com/intl/zh_hk/about/banks/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpay.google.com%2Fintl%2Fzh_hk%2Fabout%2Fbanks%2F&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1e98451e\" target=\"_blank\">https://pay.google.com/intl/zh_hk/about/banks/</a><br />\n<br />\nSamsung Pay: 參與的銀行、發卡機構及卡網絡<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.samsung.com/hk/samsungpay/#pay-enjoy-merchants\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Fhk%2Fsamsungpay%2F%23pay-enjoy-merchants&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=af9777c7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.samsung.com/hk/samsungpay/#pay-enjoy-merchants</a><br />\n<br />\nTTRate<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.ttrate.com/zh_hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ttrate.com%2Fzh_hk%2F&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1da6830c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ttrate.com/zh_hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fe702a86e97e8a1d2fcdebb856cee85ccfa5791","tid":735623,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:31:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#2 集中討論卡種</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Asia Miles</div><br />\n<br />\n- DBS<br />\n<img src=\"https://gobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net/hk/creditcards/e3d9c739-aeed-41dc-9424-6de93ab1d7d2.jpg?width=200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net%2Fhk%2Fcreditcards%2Fe3d9c739-aeed-41dc-9424-6de93ab1d7d2.jpg%3Fwidth%3D200&h=bd82da62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBlack World Mastercard：本地 $6/里、外幣 $4/里、AAVS $12/里<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：年薪 $240K／大專生 (需先申請 COMPASS VISA，詳見 #4)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：DCC 冇分</span><br />\n<br />\n- HSBC<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hsbc.com.hk/pws/Components/personal/assets/images/cards_visa_signature_card_t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsbc.com.hk%2Fpws%2FComponents%2Fpersonal%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fcards_visa_signature_card_t.jpg&h=c4c09712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVisa Signature：最紅自主獎賞 $2.78&ndash;4.17/里、網上 $4.17/里*、AAVS $25/里<br />\n其他：最紅自主獎賞 $4.17/里、網上 $4.17/里*、AAVS $25/里<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻 (Visa Signature)：年薪 $480K／$600K 資產</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻 (其他)：年薪 $60K+</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：唔中最紅自主回贈率低</span><br />\n<br />\n- Standard Chartered Bank<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sc.com/global/av/forms/d1/assets/product/credit-cards-asia-mile-hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sc.com%2Fglobal%2Fav%2Fforms%2Fd1%2Fassets%2Fproduct%2Fcredit-cards-asia-mile-hd.jpg&h=60f188a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAsia Miles：$6/里 (AAVS)、食肆／網上／外幣 $4/里<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：年薪 $240K／$80K 渣打戶口存款</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：DCC 1% 手續費</span>"},{"pid":"af62629ec0e98edf15dc566bb2b7f4cad8448fdb","tid":735623,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Avios</div><br />\n<br />\n- Dah Sing Bank<br />\n<img src=\"https://gobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net/sg-acc/creditcardsv2/3ddc7bb6-0e3c-42c0-bd1a-69339923a04e.png?width=160\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net%2Fsg-acc%2Fcreditcardsv2%2F3ddc7bb6-0e3c-42c0-bd1a-69339923a04e.png%3Fwidth%3D160&h=ca856fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBA: $6/Avios (AAVS)、外幣 $4/Avios<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：$150K</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：Apple Pay 簽賬唔計迎新</span><br />\n<br />\n- DBS<br />\n<img src=\"https://gobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net/hk/creditcards/e3d9c739-aeed-41dc-9424-6de93ab1d7d2.jpg?width=200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net%2Fhk%2Fcreditcards%2Fe3d9c739-aeed-41dc-9424-6de93ab1d7d2.jpg%3Fwidth%3D200&h=bd82da62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBlack World Mastercard：本地 $6/Avios、外幣 $4/Avios、AAVS $12/Avios<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：年薪 $240K／大專生 (需先申請 COMPASS VISA，詳見 #4)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：DCC 冇分</span><br />\n<br />\n- HSBC<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hsbc.com.hk/pws/Components/personal/assets/images/credit-cards/HSBC_Premier_World_Mastercard_HK_RGB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsbc.com.hk%2Fpws%2FComponents%2Fpersonal%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fcredit-cards%2FHSBC_Premier_World_Mastercard_HK_RGB.jpg&h=d0c5d621&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPremier：最紅自主獎賞 $2.78/Avios、網上 $2.78/Avios<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：$1M 滙豐卓越理財資產</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：門檻高</span>"},{"pid":"3b3643bf172ad355c2b0e1bc44a4a010d56048ae","tid":735623,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:31:49.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">積分 (1X = 0.4% 回贈／$15/里)</div><br />\n<br />\n- Bank of China, Hong Kong<br />\n<img src=\"https://gobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net/hk/creditcards/3fbd7513-7a0b-4548-b090-f6c1f4459503.jpg?width=220\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net%2Fhk%2Fcreditcards%2F3fbd7513-7a0b-4548-b090-f6c1f4459503.jpg%3Fwidth%3D220&h=9eb3cbec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ni-card：每月頭 $1,111.12 網上／流動付款 (e.g.  Pay) 10X (分開計)<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：年薪 $150K／大專生</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：10X 每月上限好快爆、積分有效期 &lt; 2 年</span><br />\n<br />\n- China Construction Bank<br />\n<img src=\"https://gobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net/sg-acc/creditcardsv2/e551dccd-e46f-40ee-91a2-31a2a82d4891.jpg?width=180\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net%2Fsg-acc%2Fcreditcardsv2%2Fe551dccd-e46f-40ee-91a2-31a2a82d4891.jpg%3Fwidth%3D180&h=abe246ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\neye Card：網上／payWave 5X、旅遊／外幣額外 2X<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：年薪 $150K</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：積分有效期 &lt; 2 年</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">現金回贈</div><br />\n<br />\n- Bank of China<br />\n<img src=\"https://blog-cdn.moneysmart.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/boci-dai-wan1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog-cdn.moneysmart.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fboci-dai-wan1.png&h=34f268d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大灣區一卡通 (鑽石卡)：每月頭 $2,500 銀聯閃付 4%<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：年薪 $200K／大專生 (需先申請其他中銀大專生卡，詳見 #4)</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：閃付經常交易失敗</span><br />\n<br />\n- HSBC<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hsbc.com.hk/pws/Components/personal/assets/images/cards_visa_signature_card_t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hsbc.com.hk%2Fpws%2FComponents%2Fpersonal%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fcards_visa_signature_card_t.jpg&h=c4c09712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nVisa Signature：最紅自主獎賞 3.6%、網上 2.4%*、AAVS 0.4%<br />\n其他：最紅自主獎賞 2.4%、網上 2.4%*、AAVS 0.4%<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻 (Visa Signature)：年薪 $480K／$600K 資產</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻 (其他)：年薪 $60K+</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：唔中最紅自主回贈率低</span><br />\n<br />\n- ICBC<br />\n<img src=\"http://v.icbc.com.cn/userfiles/Resources/ICBC/haiwai/Asia/photo/2018/horoscope_visasignature_cardface_v2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fv.icbc.com.cn%2Fuserfiles%2FResources%2FICBC%2Fhaiwai%2FAsia%2Fphoto%2F2018%2Fhoroscope_visasignature_cardface_v2.jpg&h=d961f195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宇宙星座卡 : 1.5% (AAVS)<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：年薪 $250K／大專生</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：成個月都未收到卡、冇  Pay</span><br />\n<br />\n- Standard Chartered<br />\n<img src=\"https://gobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net/hk/creditcardsv2/7dbbb355-8094-4d89-ac10-598bf132548d.png?width=180\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net%2Fhk%2Fcreditcardsv2%2F7dbbb355-8094-4d89-ac10-598bf132548d.png%3Fwidth%3D180&h=58bc6c0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSimply Cash：本地 1.5% (AAVS)、外幣 2%<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：年薪 $240K</span><br />\n<br />\n- 中信<br />\nMotion：2% (AAVS)<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：年薪 $150K</span><br />\n<br />\n- 安信<br />\nEarnMORE 銀聯鑽石卡：2% (AAVS)<br />\n<img src=\"https://gobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net/hk/creditcards/e832cc4c-88c3-47be-8dbf-98dd1c3f4ae2.jpg?width=200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net%2Fhk%2Fcreditcards%2Fe832cc4c-88c3-47be-8dbf-98dd1c3f4ae2.jpg%3Fwidth%3D200&h=09d97c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：年薪 $150K／大專生</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：比較少商戶收銀聯，尤其係海外</span><br />\n<br />\nWeWa 銀聯鑽石卡：指定類別 4%&ndash;6%<br />\n<img src=\"https://gobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net/hk/creditcards/518a56e4-344a-4f50-bdf9-befadc08f2d8.jpg?width=200\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgobear-images-cdn.azureedge.net%2Fhk%2Fcreditcards%2F518a56e4-344a-4f50-bdf9-befadc08f2d8.jpg%3Fwidth%3D200&h=e4ee06dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">門檻：年薪 $150K／大專生</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">弱點：比較少商戶收銀聯，尤其係海外</span><br />\n<br />\n*：有最低消費<br />\n<br />\n- 申請門檻僅供參考，銀行保留最終決定權"},{"pid":"e4be6f53f9c79c0ba883dc29e3d5d8cfb5e11af0","tid":735623,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:32:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#3 大學生懶人包</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(以下所有卡都用學生證／Share Limit 大法就開到)</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Part 1 : 現金回贈類</span><br />\n<br />\n&middot; 中銀 i-card + 大灣鑽石銀聯<br />\n&middot; 安信 EarnMORE 銀聯 + WeWa Visa<br />\n&middot; ICBC 星座 Visa Signature<br />\n<br />\n<ins>用法</ins><br />\n<br />\ni-card：每月頭 $1,111 拍卡 (Apple Pay、Google Pay 都計)／$1,111 網上 10X 分 (4% 回贈)<br />\n<br />\n大灣鑽石銀聯：每月頭 $2,500 閃付 4% 回贈<br />\n<br />\nWeWa：食飯／海外 - 過 $400 可以玩 Shake Shake&amp;nbsp;回贈，最多有6% (基本上玩親都係 15X = 6%)<br />\n唱 K 有 4% 回贈<br />\n<br />\nEarnMORE 銀聯 + ICBC 星座 VS： 補位神卡<br />\n以上所講嘅類別以外嘅簽賬，就靠依兩張<br />\n收銀聯就簽 EarnMORE：2%回贈<br />\n唔收就簽 ICBC 星座 VS：1.5% 回贈<br />\n<br />\n<ins>同場加映</ins><br />\n<br />\nBEA i-Titanium：月份簽賬滿 $1,800，當中網上簽帳有 3% 回贈<br />\n(經常簽網上過$1,800 者可考慮此卡)<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Part 2 : 里數類</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n(以下只講 Asia Miles，學生想玩 Avios 已有 DBS BWC 同大新 BA)<br />\n<br />\n&middot; DBS Black World Mastercard (DBS BWC)<br />\n&middot; American Express Cathay Pacific Elite Credit Card (CX AE)<br />\n&middot; 中銀 i-card<br />\n<br />\n<ins>用法</ins><br />\n<br />\nDBS BWC : 本地 $6/里、海外 $4/里<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCX AE : 本地 $6/里、海外 $4/里<br />\n可入 lounge<br />\n<br />\ni-card：每月頭 $1,111 拍卡 (Apple Pay、Google Pay 都計)／$1,111 網上 10X 分 ($1.5/里)"},{"pid":"b3a5bc7aa6dd6ec9f958ac709696ab59c026c057","tid":735623,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:32:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#4 教學類文章</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">DBS 開 Black / Eminent (共用信用額)</span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n條件：成功批核任何一張 DBS 信用卡，並已啟動 DBS iBanking 網上理財<br />\n<br />\nStep 1：登入 DBS iBanking 網上理財<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/193529_1040f18ab1ec419e59504721a8b7860b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F193529_1040f18ab1ec419e59504721a8b7860b.png&h=4c9f6a7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nStep 2：於信用卡一欄，按「申請信用卡」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/193647_14b6beec3a556a7f8dcc48258adda508.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F193647_14b6beec3a556a7f8dcc48258adda508.png&h=cf2f7bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nStep 3：短訊認證後，便可選擇想申請的信用卡類別<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/193808_7444be6232c9ed47518a4ee9645e64a7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F193808_7444be6232c9ed47518a4ee9645e64a7.png&h=38498861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中銀開大灣區一卡通 (共用信用額)</span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n條件：成功批核任何一張中銀信用卡，並已啟動網上銀行<br />\n<br />\nStep 1：登入網上銀行<br />\n<br />\nStep 2：於信用卡一欄，按「申請信用卡」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/201250_30daecf877170d17480cff3042b0ff34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F201250_30daecf877170d17480cff3042b0ff34.png&h=ca434582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nStep 3：選擇「中銀雙幣卡大灣區一卡通」的雙幣鑽石卡並按「申請」，再按頁面指示完成<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/14/201444_fb89195e51039f548d925da8729368e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F14%2F201444_fb89195e51039f548d925da8729368e5.png&h=1f952253&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">繳交學費回贈</span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<ins>持有恆生大學聯營信用卡 (中大，城大，浸大，恆大)</ins><br />\n<br />\n請參考 &ldquo;中大資訊&rdquo; Facebook Page 教學<br />\n<br />\nStep 1：登記「高達5x Cash Dollars自我增值獎賞」<br />\n<a href=\"http://cuhkinfo.blogspot.hk/2013/07/blog-post_21.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcuhkinfo.blogspot.hk%2F2013%2F07%2Fblog-post_21.html&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c324837f\" target=\"_blank\">http://cuhkinfo.blogspot.hk/2013/07/blog-post_21.html</a><br />\n<br />\nStep 2：登入個人e-Banking 繳費<br />\n<a href=\"http://cuhkinfo.blogspot.hk/2017/09/blog-post_20.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcuhkinfo.blogspot.hk%2F2017%2F09%2Fblog-post_20.html&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5427af30\" target=\"_blank\">http://cuhkinfo.blogspot.hk/2017/09/blog-post_20.html</a><br />\n<br />\n鳴謝：中大資訊Page<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>其他信用卡</strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n常用繳費信用卡 (接受大學生申請) 包括：<br />\n1. 恆生 enJoy (0.5% Cash Dollar)<br />\n2. 中銀 i-card (0.4% rebate)<br />\n<br />\n恆生 enJoy 繳費方法請參考 持有恆生大學聯營信用卡 Step 2<br />\n<br />\n中銀網上銀行繳費步驟：<br />\n<br />\nStep 1：登入網上銀行<br />\n<br />\nStep 2：於「信用卡」一欄按「繳付賬單」<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/07/P7voKw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2FP7voKw.png&h=91bd4fac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nStep 3：按「繳付新賬單」<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/07/ySuv1P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2FySuv1P.png&h=5a65b7e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nStep 4：按頁面所示輸入繳費資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/07/YWzSLc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2FYWzSLc.png&h=da3f8b25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29ff879936c492324b16f6800878e3f507fc1ba4","tid":735623,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"唔知原來自己係1001<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30264536b62c717db963e83f7ec85026b56f4b3","tid":735623,"uid":138999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29ff879936c492324b16f6800878e3f507fc1ba4","tid":735623,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"唔知原來自己係1001<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"唔係post 42喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa6a062a321f917015ef2572d1bf47633013b89","tid":735623,"uid":120461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:47:47.000Z","msg":"有無人申請過ICBC果張line friends 卡？等左幾耐先有卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2a19bf2cb5130621b9f575b6607fb26b66a0f0","tid":735623,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c30264536b62c717db963e83f7ec85026b56f4b3","tid":735623,"uid":138999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29ff879936c492324b16f6800878e3f507fc1ba4","tid":735623,"uid":38098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"唔知原來自己係1001<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"唔係post 42喇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:47:57.000Z","msg":"OH唔記得改, 下個POST轉返43"},{"pid":"7a49b18d43d0396aacb25703c1ed484cb4772ac1","tid":735623,"uid":40381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:48:51.000Z","msg":"如果有500k cash and 股 開唔開到hsbc vs<br />\n本身有 白金卡"},{"pid":"bbb2247c988cfb4a6abc5a3564712f236dec92b2","tid":735623,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T15:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins>目錄</ins><br />\n<br />\n#1 FAQ<br />\n#2 集中討論卡種<br />\n#3 大學生懶人包<br />\n#4 教學<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">借定唔借，還得到先好借！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<em>世上冇免費午餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學賺回贈前，先爬文做功課 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </em></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#1 FAQ</span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ：年薪 $1,000,000 申請咩卡好？<br />\nA：八達通卡<br />\n<br />\nQ：想求 Member-Get-Member (MGM) 推薦連結應該點做？<br />\nA：留低自己嘅聯絡分式 (e.g. Telegram)，<span style=\"color: red;\">重申本 post 嚴禁貼 MGM link</span><br />\n<br />\nQ：點申請年費豁免？<br />\nA：(1) 先致電年費豁免或客戶服務熱線 (2) 如未能豁免可考慮取消信用卡<br />\n<em>(收年費後一個月內取消，卡行一定會回水)</em><br />\n<br />\nQ：邊張卡啱我用／回贈高啲？<br />\nA：消費習慣因人而異，請自行比較<br />\n<br />\nQ：邊張卡 O! ePay／PayMe／WeChat Pay／支付寶HK 有分？<br />\nA：Google<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ：八達通自動增值 (AAVS)、網上繳費用邊張好？<br />\nA：睇<ins>集中討論卡種</ins><br />\n<br />\nQ：迎新／推廣嘅里數／積分／回贈幾時先有？<br />\nA：睇 T&amp;C<br />\n<br />\nQ：點解有啲卡你地唔講嘅？<br />\nA：狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">渣打</div></span></strong></span><br />\nQ：究竟 PayMe／WeChat Pay／支付寶HK 有冇分？<br />\nA：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">安信</div></span></strong></span><br />\nQ：有冇得申請返 Visa？<br />\nA：<a href=\"https://m.primecredit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/WeWa-Visa-PDF-form-FA.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.primecredit.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2FWeWa-Visa-PDF-form-FA.pdf&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=36906603\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.primecredit.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/WeWa-Visa-PDF-form-FA.pdf</a> (適用於全新／現有客戶)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">實用 Link</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n💳 信用卡討論區 (41) 貼link死全家 年費免問 發問前睇#1<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/724035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/724035</a><br />\n<br />\nApple Pay: 特約銀行和發卡機構<br />\n<a href=\"https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT206638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fzh-hk%2FHT206638&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=58cd5c24\" target=\"_blank\">https://support.apple.com/zh-hk/HT206638</a><br />\n<br />\nGoogle Pay： 合作銀行<br />\n<a href=\"https://pay.google.com/intl/zh_hk/about/banks/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpay.google.com%2Fintl%2Fzh_hk%2Fabout%2Fbanks%2F&d=XR3EqJ4lS%2B5xJk8GsSrWCqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1e98451e\" target=\"_blank\">https://pay.google.com/intl/zh_hk/about/banks/</a><br />\n<br />\nSamsung Pay: 參與的銀行、發卡機構及卡網絡<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.samsung.com/hk/samsungpay/#pay-enjoy-merchants\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=